oneway.name: Lufthansa
oneway.desc_flight: Airline protected transfersIf you miss a transfer and it's covered by the airline, contact the airline directly.Missed a connection? Depending on their T&Cs, the airline may offer you:  	Another flight to your destination	Hotel, food and drinks during long layovers 	A refund	 Contact the airline:	Try to find the airline’s check-in counter at the airport	Call them or open a Live Chat session on their website	Have your e-ticket ready — they may ask you for your PNR Number	 Baggage :	Maximum 35 KG allowed for in plane transfer 	the handy baggage should be not more then 15 KG 	 We do not apply to this type of transfer because it’s already covered by the airline.
